{"about_the_game":"Embark on a side-splitting adventure in SideQuest: Reanimated, a side-scrolling action RPG set in the enchanting world of Mederlund. Follow the uproarious escapades of a delightfully unconventional band of heroes. You'll enjoy strategic combat, a wealth of unique quests, and deeply customizable character builds.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">TAKE ON CHALLENGING (AND FUNNY!) QUESTS</h2><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1711470/extras/SideQuest_About_This_Game.gif?t=1721601785\" /><br><br>As the name suggests, there\u2019s no shortage of quests in Sidequest! Discover hilarious NPCs, defeat cool bosses and navigate a huge number of quests - many of them with unique challenges and minigames for you to conquer.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">CHOOSE FROM 5 PLAYABLE CHARACTERS</h2><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1711470/extras/PuzzleGate.gif?t=1721601785\" /><br><br>Choose from 5 playable characters - each one with unique abilities, looks and personality! Each character has 2 talent builds to choose from - so whether looking to be a damage dealer, tank or support, there\u2019s a character for you.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">DEEP CUSTOMIZATION AND ONE-OF-A-KIND BUILDS</h2><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1711470/extras/Outfits.gif?t=1721601785\" /><br><br>Feeling creative? Craft your own path to victory with hugely customizable characters - choosing their abilities, stats and gear to come up with unique synergies and builds! Choose your own playstyle - and create builds that nobody has ever seen before!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">EMBARK SOLO OR WITH FRIENDS</h2><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1711470/extras/Gambler.gif?t=1721601785\" /><br><br>You\u2019re never alone in Sidequest - whether you embark solo with your NPC companions joining you, or whether you play multiplayer co-op with your friends, you\u2019ll always have a party by your side!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">FEATURES:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>30+ quests planned for release!<br></li><li>Choose from 5 playable characters, each one with 2 talent builds!<br></li><li>20+ different enemy types.<br></li><li>A deep progression system of loot, upgrades and skills!<br></li><li>Multiplayer and single-player capabilities.<br></li><li>Unique, funny dialogue and NPCs to discover!</li></ul><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1711470/extras/SideQuest_Wishlist_Now.gif?t=1721601785\" />","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1711470/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1721601785","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1711470/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1721601785","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1711470/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1721601785","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1711470/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1721601785","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Multi-player","id":1},{"description":"PvP","id":49},{"description":"Online PvP","id":36},{"description":"Co-op","id":9},{"description":"Online Co-op","id":38}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[1,5],"notes":null},"demos":[{"appid":2525520,"description":""}],"detailed_description":"Embark on a side-splitting adventure in SideQuest: Reanimated, a side-scrolling action RPG set in the enchanting world of Mederlund. Follow the uproarious escapades of a delightfully unconventional band of heroes. You'll enjoy strategic combat, a wealth of unique quests, and deeply customizable character builds.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">TAKE ON CHALLENGING (AND FUNNY!) QUESTS</h2><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1711470/extr